ford27岁，母亲Mrs. Hugh Sanford22岁。她于1267年与William Jenkinus Leighton在英国越可爾利德斯结婚。他们至少是2个儿子和2个女儿的父母。她去世在英国英格兰史洛普爾麗頓。"},"hr":{"1247–":"1247.–preminula","1247–Female":"1247.–preminula","1243–Male":"1243–preminuo","1272–Female":"1272–preminula","1274–Male":"1274–preminuo","1275–Male":"1275.–preminuo","1280–Female":"1280–preminula","1221–Male":"1221–preminuo","1225–Female":"1225–preminula","about 1272":"oko 1272.","about 1280":"oko 1280.","1275":"1275.","1274":"1274","1272":"1272","abt 1299":"oko 1274.","1280":"1280","1290":"1290","1315":"1315","1259":"1259","1247":"1247.","1225":"1225","1267":"1267.","1221":"1221","1243":"1243","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Leeds, West Yorkshire, England":"Leeds, West Yorkshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Thornton Mayow, Cheshire, England":"Thornton Mayow, Cheshire, England","Leighton, Shropshire, England":"Leighton, Shropshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Leeds, Yorkshire, England":"Leeds, Yorkshire, England"},"cs":{"1247–":"1247–Zesnulá","1247–Female":"1247–Zesnulá","1243–Male":"1243–Zesnulý","1272–Female":"1272–Zesnulá","1274–Male":"1274–Zesnulý","1275–Male":"1275–Zesnulý","1280–Female":"1280–Zesnulá","1221–Male":"1221–Zesnulý","1225–Female":"1225–Zesnulá","about 1272":"okolo 1272","about 1280":"okolo 1280","1275":"1275","1274":"1274","1272":"1272","abt 1299":"okolo 1274","1280":"1280","1290":"1290","1315":"1315","1259":"1259","1247":"1247","1225":"1225","1267":"1267","1221":"1221","1243":"1243","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Leeds, West Yorkshire, England":"Leeds, West Yorkshire, Anglie, United Kingdom","Thornton Mayow, Cheshire, England":"Thornton Mayow, Cheshire, Anglie","Leighton, Shropshire, England":"Leighton, Shropshire, Anglie, United Kingdom","Leeds, Yorkshire, England":"Leeds, Yorkshire, Anglie"},"da":{"1247–":"1247–Afdød","1247–Female":"1247–Afdød","1243–Male":"1243–Afdød","1272–Female":"1272–Afdød","1274–Male":"1274–Afdød","1275–Male":"1275–Afdød","1280–Female":"1280–Afdød","1221–Male":"1221–Afdød","1225–Female":"1225–Afdød","abou